    id: 'prompt-34',
    prompt: 'Plan and schedule a weekly spiritual preparation review session by setting aside 30 minutes every Sunday to assess your spiritual practices, plan the upcoming week, and adjust your spiritual goals as needed',
    category: 'planning',
    helpText: 'Regular spiritual planning sessions help you maintain intentional growth by creating space to evaluate what\'s working and adjust your approach based on real experience. Use this weekly time to review which practices served you well, identify spiritual challenges you encountered, and plan specific spiritual activities for the coming week that align with your current needs and growth goals. This consistent planning habit ensures your spiritual development stays responsive to your evolving needs while maintaining steady progress toward your larger spiritual aspirations.'
  }</parameter>
<parameter name="new_string">  {
