    helpText: 'Moving from spiritual understanding to actual implementation requires choosing specific, measurable actions that can be repeated consistently to build lasting spiritual habits. Select one practice that feels both meaningful and achievable within your daily routine, then commit to the same time each day to create automatic behavioral patterns. This focused implementation approach helps transform spiritual insights into lived experience while building the discipline and consistency needed for sustained spiritual growth and transformation.'
